Body:
Description: Hello team,

We are facing an issue where two admins from the admin group synced with EPP still appear as Usertype: EPP and not an AD one, they are also unable to use the password on the AD to login. I will attach a print for you.

Best regards,

What We've Learned Updated: 2 AD users are not syncing correctly and are not able to log in using the AD password.
Initial troubleshooting was performed by the partner with a negative outcome.
Next Steps Updated: SSH into the server and delete the users from the DB and try the sync again
